There are better weapons out on dmg/del and stats ratio.<br>
<br>
I used for a few solo fights (which I rarely do), the sword can, but will not always turn the tide. At 151 dex at level 57 vs bllue Mobs it's quite nice. On avrage it procs around 4 times per fight, that's 600hp for you and 600hp less for mob, but it is random and as such, a certain amount of risk is involved.<br>
I prefer to use it when in groups, where I might get a little dmg even when not MT, such as in OS. <p><div align="center"><font size="2"><i><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif"><b><font color="#CCCCCC">Drachan 
